### Create Department first (MongoDB)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/mongo/departments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "IT Department"
}

###

### Create another Department (MongoDB)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/mongo/departments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "HR Department"
}

###

### Get All Departments (MongoDB)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/mongo/departments
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Department by Name (MongoDB)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/mongo/departments/search/name?name=IT Department
Accept: application/json

###

### Create Employee with Department (MongoDB)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/mongo/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nguyen Van A",
  "dob": "1990-01-15",
  "salary": 15000000,
  "department": {
    "id": "DEPARTMENT_ID_HERE"
  }
}

###

### Create another Employee (MongoDB)
