###

### 1. Tìm tất cả nhân viên (MongoDB)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/mongo/employees
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Tìm nhân viên theo mã (ID) (MongoDB)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/mongo/employees/EMPLOYEE_ID_HERE
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Tìm nhân viên theo tên (MongoDB)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/mongo/employees/search/name?name=Nguyen
Accept: application/json

###

### Tìm nhân viên theo tên (case insensitive) (MongoDB)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/mongo/employees/search/name?name=van
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Tìm danh sách nhân viên theo phòng ban (theo ID) (MongoDB)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/mongo/employees/search/department/DEPARTMENT_ID_HERE
Accept: application/json

###

### Tìm danh sách nhân viên theo tên phòng ban (MongoDB)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/mongo/employees/search/department?departmentName=IT Department
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Tìm nhân viên theo khoảng lương (10-16 triệu) (MongoDB)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/mongo/employees/search/salary/range?minSalary=10000000&maxSalary=16000000
Accept: application/json

###

### Tìm nhân viên có lương >= 15 triệu (MongoDB)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/mongo/employees/search/salary/min?salary=15000000
Accept: application/json

###

### Tìm nhân viên có lương <= 15 triệu (MongoDB)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/mongo/employees/search/salary/max?salary=15000000
Accept: application/json

###

### Update Employee (MongoDB)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/mongo/employees/EMPLOYEE_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nguyen Van A Updated",
  "dob": "1990-01-15",
  "salary": 20000000,
  "department": {
    "id": "DEPARTMENT_ID_HERE"
  }
}

###

### Delete Employee (MongoDB)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/mongo/employees/EMPLOYEE_ID_HERE

###

### Delete Department (MongoDB)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/mongo/departments/DEPARTMENT_ID_HERE

